<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/master.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/studySearch.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/css/progressBar.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bowser/2.11.0/bundled.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/studySearch.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/registerClicks.js"></script>
    <script src="/scripts/registries.js"></script>
    <title>ALEX</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include('../../partials/header'); %>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="progress-container">
            <div class="progress" id="progress"> </div>
            <div class="circle visited">✓ <br/> Background</div>
            <div class="circle visited">✓ <br/> Preferences</div>
            <div class="circle active">3  <br/>Registries</div>
            <div class="circle">4 <br/>Studies</div>
          </div>
        <h1 class="title" id="loaded-title">Your Results are Loading ...</h1>       
        <p id = "disabled-text">Thank you for that information! Your tailored list of clinical trials are loading. This may take up to 30 seconds...</p>
        <a href="/<%=id%>/<%=type%>/StudySearch/Results">
            <button id = "results" disabled class = "disabled">Loading...</button>
        </a> 
        <p>While we load your custom list of research studies, you can read about research registries -- which are special lists gathering information from people like you interested in research participation -- suitable for you, and choose to join!</p>
        <div class="study-card">
            <h3>JAX-ASCENT Registry</h3>
            <h4>Official Title:</h4>
            <p>JAX-ASCENT Registry</p>
            <hr/>
            <h4>Brief Summary*:</h4>
            <p>The JAX-ASCENT Registry is looking for adults 60 and older to join and help the University of Florida College of Medicine – Jacksonville explore aging and independence. Participants can take part in various studies, from assessing risk factors to prevention therapies, and will receive information about the latest research. There is no cost to join and compensation may be provided for time and transportation if you choose to participate in a study</p>
            <hr/>
            <h4>Keywords(s):</h4>
            <p>Older Adult, Aging</p>
            <hr/>
            <h4>How to Join:</h4>
            <p>Complete the enrollment form at UFJaxAgingStudy.com. If you have questions, call (866) 386-7730.</p>
            <a class="center" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" onclick="sendToDatabase(`RegistriesCompleteEnrollmentForm`, `clicked`)" href="http://ufjaxagingstudy.com/">
                <button>Complete Enrollment Form</button>
            </a>
            
        </div>

        <p>* This summary was prepared by the ALEX Research Team. See the full study description at: <a href="https://med.jax.ufl.edu/institute-population-health/projects-and-initiatives/jaxascent-registry/">https://med.jax.ufl.edu/institute-population-health/projects-and-initiatives/jaxascent-registry/</a></p>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>